aints on the most important\ncosmological parameters derived from Planck CMB data, including the high\nredshift dark energy abundance, by a factor \\sim 1.5.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 27 Jul 2009 20:00:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 1 Sep 2009 16:34:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-09-01"}
