 achieve scalability and resource sharing among CDNs through\neffective peering in a user transparent manner, thus evolving past the current\nlandscape where non-cooperative and distinct CDNs exist.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 28 Jul 2009 10:02:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-07-29"}
